				<img src="http://api.tweetmeme.com/imagebutton.gif?url=http%3A%2F%2Ffr.readwriteweb.com%2F2011%2F01%2F15%2Fa-la-une%2Feot-readwriteweb-france-francophonie-final-frontier%2F&amp;source=rwwfr&amp;style=normal&amp;service=bit.ly" height="61" width="50" />
