				<img src="http://api.tweetmeme.com/imagebutton.gif?url=http%3A%2F%2Ffr.readwriteweb.com%2F2011%2F01%2F05%2Fanalyse%2Fles-anonymous-sattaquent-gouvernement-tunisien-celui-du-zimbabwe%2F&amp;source=rwwfr&amp;style=normal&amp;service=bit.ly" height="61" width="50" />
